description.0: As Psylocke's condition continues to worsen, Archangel and Wolverine must venture to the Ebon Vein of the mystical realm. Will the two heroes, along with an astral Doctor Strange, be able to save Psylocke in time?
description.1: Post, "the faithful extension of Onslaught", nearly destroys Cyclops' team in battle. After Cyclops is incapacitated, his teammates rush to his aid. Plus, Professor Xavier has a strange encounter with Gateway!
description.2: Two Spiders are better than one! Ben Reilly and Peter Parker put their brains together to figure out the mystery of the Spider-Skeleton, but they'll have to go through the new Doc Ock to do it!
description.6: Imprisoned by the Imperial forces, confronted by two very violent, very massive creatures known as Yuzzem, Luke and Leia have only one hope of escape: the Mimban Crystal, capable of giving its wielder total, omnipotent mastery of the Force. But Luke's use of the crystal could draw the unwelcome attention of certain ... dark powers.
description.7: Everyone hopes to get a big break someday, move up to the top seat in their line of work. But when that line of work is intergalactic crime, you've got to make your own breaks.'Bib Fortuna,'Jabba's loyal lieutenant, has plotted a slave revolt against the'Hutt. We've seen how Jabba handles negotiations, now we'll see how he handles betrayal!
description.8: Tombstone decides to kill the mayor of New York!
description.9: The Battle of Endor (from Return of the Jedi) was never fought -- it was just so much Alliance propaganda. At least, that's the lie being spread by members of the AEA (Ante-Endor Association). But Wedge Antilles and his Rogue Squadron comrades know the truth. They were at Endor when so many of their friends and colleagues gave their lives to destroy the second Death Star. And so, for those lost friends, this is a battle they will not fail.
description.10: Strange returns home to the Midwest! Not all is bright and cheery however…
description.13: Wolverine awakens in the Princess Bar to utter devastation. Will Logan lose everyone he’s known and loved? Tyger Tiger guest-stars, aiding Wolverine in his darkest moment yet!
description.15: Brian Braddock dreams of the year 2013 -- where he finds Excalibur and England in mass chaos!
description.16: Transforming back to the Hulk saves Banner from a deadly explosion, but with a stunning cost - reverting back into Banner's body will kill him! Only one mind on Earth can solve this crisis - one of Hulk's oldest foes, the Leader!
description.17: Tony Stark must fight his younger self!
description.18: The ratings are in! The audience for Mysterio's TV-brainwashing MysteryVision continues to grow.
description.19: A new villain has taken up the Goblin name and attacks Spider-Man, but the new Goblin has much more sinister plans for Spider-Man than it seems. Things are about to change for Miguel O'Hara.
description.20: Thor and Amora awaken to find their godlike powers entirely gone! Will Black Widow rescind her invitation for Thor to join the Avengers?
description.21: Spidey reignites his powerful team up with the Human Torch to defeat the Wizard and his gaggle of weaponized robots.
description.23: STRANGE DAYS PART 4 Doctor Doom teams-up with the FF in the climactic finale to Strange Days! Will their combined might be enough to eliminate Hyperstorm? And what happens if Hyperstorm succeeds?
description.24: Doctor Strange summons the X-Men after witnessing mysterious forces in his "scrying pool." While perusing Chinatown for a miracle elixir to aid Psylocke, Angel and Wolverine encounter these forces head-on. What demons have breached this dimension? And will the two X-Men be able to handle the threat by themselves?
description.26: THE RETURN OF KAINE starts here! Spider-Man saw Kaine die a hero's death, so how has the wayward clone returned to life? And will he be friend…or foe?
description.29: X-Man vs. Excalibur on Muir Island! Nate Grey has no love for Professor Xavier. So what will he do when he discovers that Moira MacTaggert has been communing with "the enemy" all along?
description.37: He has traveled through space and time for untold ages, with a hundred different minds woven into his being. His long odyssey has eroded his memory, with no knowledge of his past or people. All he knows is that his name…is Century!
description.38: He is madness. He is chaos. He is CARNAGE! Now, one man will peer into the blackened soul of Cletus Kasady, determined to uncover the forces that drive his maniacal lusts, and attempt the impossible: the rehabilitation of Carnage!
description.39: It's Spider-Man vs. Mysterio, Round 2 - in the middle of a bitingly cold New York blizzard!
description.40: Steve Marlowe is gunning for the police chief, and it's up to Spider-Man to stop him! But unbeknownst to the wall-crawler, a mysterious schemer has called a hit on him, and the man carrying it out is none other than Frank Castle, AKA The Punisher!
description.41: FINAL ISSUE! Ben Reilly has gone from Scarlet Spider to the Amazing Spider-Man, and he must team up with the New Warriors to defeat the impostor Scarlet Spider once and for all!
description.42: TENDRIL strikes! This monstrous new foe will take all of Spider-Man's strength to defeat, but how will he react when he learns that Tendril's existence is all his fault!?
description.45: Before the X-Men…before Wolverine…before Weapon X…there was only the man named Logan.
description.46: Better change the channel - Mysterio has taken over the airwaves, and with his new TV network MysteryVision, he turns anyone who watches into his mindless henchmen!
description.47: Kang sets his final plans into motion as a teenaged Tony Stark lies dying. Will the Avengers be able to save their fallen comrade? And will Kang ever restore the Avengers' timeline?
description.50: Can Ulic go through with the Sith's devious plan or will he reject the dark side?
description.51: What if the Age of Apocalypse had never ended? The mutant despot has at last been defeated, but before peace can truly be restored, an even greater threat looms on the horizon- the Devourer of Worlds, Galactus!
description.52: Mordo has been controlling Strange for almost a decade! That isn't his only secret though...
description.53: Wolverine and Jean Grey on a mission all their own! After discovering Cyber’s escape from Muir Island, Wolverine and Phoenix investigate. The two enter a ‘W.C.’, only to discover a dimensional portal! Enter Chimera!
description.54: A day on the job for two inspectors goes horribly wrong, and one is transformed into a huge, enraged muck-monster!
description.58: Luke Skywalker's'Jedi'senses have been struck blind! To make matters worse,'Grand Admiral'Thrawn'has just arranged to receive a shipment of creatures capable of pushing back the power of'the Force. Thrawn's purpose: to ambush Luke and turn him over to the'dark Jedi'Master,'Joruus C'baoth!
description.59: The New Warriors are after a new Scarlet Spider! Why is this Scarlet Spider sinister when the previous one was a force for good? And can Speedball get a handle on his turbulent powers in time to even help at all?
description.60: It's an all-new beginning for Spider-Man, but that's not Peter Parker under the mask! Say hello to Ben Reilly, the SENSATIONAL SPIDER-MAN! But this new beginning starts with an old enemy, as Spider-Man tangles with his most mesmerizing foe - Mysterio!
description.61: Look out, Scarlet Spider - here come the New Warriors! Firestar discovers that the Scarlet Spider that joined their team is an impostor, and she's determined to find the truth once and for all! But what will it cost her?
description.62: Spider-Man faces off with an all-new menace! Who or what is the Skull-Jacket? And why is it out for the wall-crawler's hide? Guest-starring the Black Cat!
description.63: The mini-series that will change Peter Parker's life forever continues! Who is Dryrot, and why is Peter the only person that can save his life? And even if he can, will he be able to endure the cost?
description.65: From Scarlet Spider...to SPIDER-MAN! Ben Reilly dons the mantle of the original wall-crawler, but soon finds it's true that with great power does come great responsibility!
description.66: The Wasp emerges from her cocoon in an insect-like form. After being kidnapped by "big brother" Tuc, Luna makes a daring escape while rescuing Moonraker from Kang. Quicksilver faces a devastating blow when Luna's rescue mission goes awry. Will this be the death of an Avenger?
description.68: Wolfsbane goes back to her hometown to confront the same Reverend who attacked her as a child.
description.69: Trapped in the body of Savage Banner! It may be Bruce Banner's body, but it has the primal rampaging mind of the Incredible Hulk!
description.70: The truth is out: Iron Man is guilty as charged!
description.71: The venomous villain known as Poison is on a rampage through New York City, and she won't stop until her kidnapped son is returned!
description.72: Kron Stone has tormented Miguel O'Hara since they were children, but they're not children anymore, and now Miguel has the power to fight back against his childhood bully. Can Miguel control his anger or will he go too far?
description.73: On Worldengine, Thor and Amora meet Price, a former Physics professor with a truly deviant past.
description.74: The Vulture has escaped from his high security prison cell, and Spider-Man is almost immediately on the scene to stop him!
description.76: STRANGE DAYS PART 3 At long last, the mysterious origin of Hyperstorm! Who is the man claiming to be the Fantastic Four's legacy? And with Reed safely returned to his own time, will Doom soon follow?
description.77: Sabretooth escapes captivity and mortally wounds Psylocke!
description.88: Nate Grey returns to his Age of Apocalypse timeline...and has an end-of-everything battle with Sugar Man!
description.91: Spidey takes the Invisible Girl out on a date -- and you better believe the Human Torch and Sub-Mariner have something to say about it!
description.98: Corsair, along with his Starjammers, must band together to defeat their enemy...The Uncreated! Empress Lilandra influences Corsair's future.
description.99: The galaxy'teeters on the brink of revolution, and'See-Threepio'and'Artoo-Detoo'are the only ones who can stop it! The'Ithorian's plan to seed a rapture-producing herb, known as'Savorium, throughout the troubled galaxy is interrupted by the power-mad dictator'Craw. Now Threepio and Artoo face a dilemma: they can defend the Ithorian's plan, and survive, or they can destroy the Ithorian's ship and cargo, at the cost of their own existence!

2.text: Two Spiders are better than one! Ben Reilly and Peter Parker put their brains together to figure out the mystery of the Spider-Skeleton, but they'll have to go through the new Doc Ock to do it!

4.text: A sinister Emplate unloads their fury, and the aftermath will be ugly…

8.text: Tombstone decides to kill the mayor of New York!

10.text: Strange returns home to the Midwest! Not all is bright and cheery however…

11.text: With a nuclear weapon ready to blow in the heart of Genosha, Cable has to figure out how to stop it - and Sugar Man - at the same time! But it seems there's a sinister figure watching things unfold from the shadows!

12.text: OPERATION REBIRTH CONCLUSION Red Skull has trapped Captain America inside the Cosmic Cube. Living in a fantasy past, Steve Rogers must return to reality if he is to thwart Skull's machinations!

13.text: Wolverine awakens in the Princess Bar to utter devastation. Will Logan lose everyone he’s known and loved? Tyger Tiger guest-stars, aiding Wolverine in his darkest moment yet!

14.text: A surprise visit from an old face throws a new curveball into Matt’s life!

18.text: The ratings are in! The audience for Mysterio's TV-brainwashing MysteryVision continues to grow.

25.text: Dark Beast devises a new plan of attack against the X-Men.

26.text: THE RETURN OF KAINE starts here! Spider-Man saw Kaine die a hero's death, so how has the wayward clone returned to life? And will he be friend…or foe?

28.text: Warpath has a shadowy (and romantic) encounter with a mutant who seems like trouble. Boom-Boom gets a daring new look, and Siryn can’t quite get Deadpool out of her head. What’s going on there?!

31.text: The Hellions, including Emplate, come fast and hard for the Gen X crew!

32.text: With Tony Stark practically on his deathbed, Pepper, Jarvis and Happy wait and stand vigil while reminiscing about Iron Man's past.

33.text: Earth’s Mightiest Heroes must convince a younger Tony Stark to join their cross-dimensional mission! Introducing Avengers from across the Multiverse!

34.text: V.I.R.G.I.L. deploys holo-constructs against the Force Works team, forcing Daniels and the Scarlet Witch to find a way to disrupt their main power source!

35.text: Previous Green Goblins are now haunting Phil Ulrich!

36.text: War Machine arrives at the Starcore Station only to be confronted by Kang's ally Dirge!

37.text: He has traveled through space and time for untold ages, with a hundred different minds woven into his being. His long odyssey has eroded his memory, with no knowledge of his past or people. All he knows is that his name…is Century!

38.text: He is madness. He is chaos. He is CARNAGE! Now, one man will peer into the blackened soul of Cletus Kasady, determined to uncover the forces that drive his maniacal lusts, and attempt the impossible: the rehabilitation of Carnage!

40.text: Steve Marlowe is gunning for the police chief, and it's up to Spider-Man to stop him! But unbeknownst to the wall-crawler, a mysterious schemer has called a hit on him, and the man carrying it out is none other than Frank Castle, AKA The Punisher!

41.text: FINAL ISSUE! Ben Reilly has gone from Scarlet Spider to the Amazing Spider-Man, and he must team up with the New Warriors to defeat the impostor Scarlet Spider once and for all!

42.text: TENDRIL strikes! This monstrous new foe will take all of Spider-Man's strength to defeat, but how will he react when he learns that Tendril's existence is all his fault!?

43.text: Ben's first clash with Venom rages on! Can the new Spidey survive against the sinister symbiote?

44.text: Storm struggles with guilt and has a too close brush with death in the debut issue of her own limited series!

45.text: Before the X-Men…before Wolverine…before Weapon X…there was only the man named Logan.

48.text: Doom comes to blows with the Driver, a motorcycle-riding mutant sympathizer.

49.text: Not even the great mutant mind of Charles Xavier can stop the Dark Phoenix!

51.text: What if the Age of Apocalypse had never ended? The mutant despot has at last been defeated, but before peace can truly be restored, an even greater threat looms on the horizon- the Devourer of Worlds, Galactus!

52.text: Mordo has been controlling Strange for almost a decade! That isn't his only secret though...

53.text: Wolverine and Jean Grey on a mission all their own! After discovering Cyber’s escape from Muir Island, Wolverine and Phoenix investigate. The two enter a ‘W.C.’, only to discover a dimensional portal! Enter Chimera!

54.text: A day on the job for two inspectors goes horribly wrong, and one is transformed into a huge, enraged muck-monster!

55.text: Omega Red has taken out all of Generation X!  Except for Chamber, that is!  Will the young lone mutant be able to defeat such a powerful enemy?

56.text: The truth behind the Genoshan civil war revealed! But can Cable, Domino and their unlikely allies bring an end to the fighting before it's too late!

57.text: OPERATION REBIRTH PART 3 Sharon Carter has stolen the Cosmic Cube, but not before it transformed a group of soldiers into a battalion of New World Reich Soldiers! Now Cap and Red Skull must face a contingent of advanced warriors from another world!

59.text: The New Warriors are after a new Scarlet Spider! Why is this Scarlet Spider sinister when the previous one was a force for good? And can Speedball get a handle on his turbulent powers in time to even help at all?

61.text: Look out, Scarlet Spider - here come the New Warriors! Firestar discovers that the Scarlet Spider that joined their team is an impostor, and she's determined to find the truth once and for all! But what will it cost her?

62.text: Spider-Man faces off with an all-new menace! Who or what is the Skull-Jacket? And why is it out for the wall-crawler's hide? Guest-starring the Black Cat!

63.text: The mini-series that will change Peter Parker's life forever continues! Who is Dryrot, and why is Peter the only person that can save his life? And even if he can, will he be able to endure the cost?

64.text: Ben Reilly's been cruising as Spider-Man, so of course it was only a matter of time before he faced down one of the wall-crawler's greatest foes! VENOM busts Anne out of prison, and Ben is the only one that can stop him!

67.text: Matt deals with the aftermath of his identity crisis!

71.text: The venomous villain known as Poison is on a rampage through New York City, and she won't stop until her kidnapped son is returned!

78.text: Since Bishop is the only one who remembers the Age of Apocalypse, Sugar Man and Dark Beast decide they must eliminate the X-Man for good.

80.text: Hawkeye reaches out to Black Widow, U.S. Agent and War Machine to help them track down Iron Man and stop Kang.

81.text: Green Goblin must take down the Hobgoblin!

82.text: War Machine does battle with Iron Man while Moonraker, Scarlet Witch, Spider-Woman, and Fisher Todd return from Vietnam.

83.text: A compilation of incredible tales starring an entirely derailed Hulk! From courtroom drama to a Captain America guest spot, this issue has it all!

84.text: Collision with the Shi'ar! Cable and his commando crew are not only dealing with a fugitive cyborg…they also have to contend with one of the galaxy’s most elite task forces!

85.text: Storm and Bishop track down Shard before a precognitive mutant can find her first!

86.text: Ten years have passed since Nathan Summers, aka Cable, defeated Apocalypse. But the past keeps colliding with the present, when Nathan is introduced to “Professor”, a mysterious man with ties to his parents. Cable listens to the legend of the X-Men, but when story-teller Fossil declares that is was Mother Askani who killed Apocalypse, Cable loses his cool.

87.text: X-Force turns on their leader! And Sage’s psy-powers might be to blame! Can Cable and Domino right this wrong before either of them are taken out…permanently?

89.text: Guest-starring Rogue! Nate helps one of the X-Men's feistiest members in battle against X-Cutioner!

90.text: The Fenris twins are back! Generation X gets caught up in a saga treading the mutant and human world.

93.text: Corrupted S.H.I.E.L.D. agents and Captain America 2099 threaten to throw the wrench in Doom’s plot to regain supremacy!

94.text: Continuing the fully-painted look at Spider-Man's first amazing adventures! Spidey swings into action against his first super-powered foe, a young mystery vandal who's a super-villain in the making! More of the good ol' days!

95.text: The Dark Phoenix has been unleashed!

96.text: Ben Reilly has just discovered that he is a clone of Peter Parker. Lost and alone, he begins to wander aimlessly in the hope that he will discover a new life and a new direction.
